column7: The pacing of the video was appropriate and was able to capture the attention of the audience.
column8: After watching the video, I understand the importance of having a work life balance while studying
column9: After watching the video, I am more aware of the different methods of adopting work-life balance
column10: Throughout the video, I agree with most of the methods that was adopt by the work and study students to achieve balance in their physical, nutrition, social and mental health
column11: Provide any other suggestions that can improve the video quality and message further?

Very well made video and info given was good! On top of that, the gifs are funny and cute. However, i think it might be slightly better with lesser gifs as it may distract the viewers to much and drift them away from the main message that you may have wanted to deliver :) but overall, good job!
The video quality could be better. Perhaps it’s due to the lighting, which makes the video at times grainy looking.
Can have a calming instrumental background music
